it.unibz.inf.be - package it.unibz.inf.be
Domain classes, representing each entity involved in the application in the same way as they is represented in the CSV files
it.unibz.inf.bl - package it.unibz.inf.bl
Classes implementing the business logic of the entire application.
The methods in these classes are called by views and access the model to modify or query it
it.unibz.inf.model - package it.unibz.inf.model
Model classes, holding the state of the application at runtime
it.unibz.inf.ui - package it.unibz.inf.ui
Classes implementing the user interface (CLI).
These classes access the model through the BL classes, i.e., they never access the model directly
